com.facebook.litho.sections

Class ChangesetDebugConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.litho.sections.ChangesetDebugConfiguration

  • public class ChangesetDebugConfiguration
extends Object
    Used for debugging changeset generation. If a ChangesetDebugConfiguration.ChangesetDebugListener instance is configured, an event will be dispatched from the SectionTree whenever a new changeset is generated and applied.
